blocks.text: The following analysis may help you understand your MAIN PROCESS FLOWS.  A first analysis can be performed using the "Process Discovery" widget, shown below, to investigate how many events and execution paths are performed. Additionally, you can switch to the "Cycle Time" metric to see which execution paths take more time during the execution.

Using the process execution path analysis you should become a better understanding of how you execute your processes. The process paths shown on top of our reference process model stress the main process flows. In addition, you find your compliance scores for the different execution steps below. Those may help you in prioritizing your topics for process improvement.
